		<h1>A View Through Some &#039;Transparent&#039; LCD Screens</h1>
		
		<h2>Want to make the screen of your laptop, tablet, or cell phone seem to disappear? Here are some inspiring examples.</h2>
		
		<p class="byline">
		By <a href="/author/Ian-Paul">Ian Paul</a>, <a href="http://www.pcworld.com/" target="_blank">PCWorld</a>
			&nbsp;&nbsp; <script type="text/javascript">timestamp(1280193300000,'longDateTime')</script>
		</p>
	
	</div> <!-- END #articleHead -->

